      <title>威兹航空预计六个月内将对印度入境计划做出回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/wizz-air-expects-response-to-india-entry-plans-in-six-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利廉价航空公司 Wizz Air Holdings Plc 预计将在未来六个月内了解其飞往该国航班计划的状态，届时该航空公司计划接收第一架可服务于该航线的空客 SE 喷气式飞机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/wizz-air-expects-response-to-india-entry-plans-in-six-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 14:36:50 GMT</pubDate>
