      <title>候选人退休以遏制极右翼势力，法国债券价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/french-bonds-gain-as-candidates-retire-to-curb-far-right-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称，在周日的第二轮选举后，各政党正在采取措施阻止极右翼获得绝对多数席位，法国债券价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/french-bonds-gain-as-candidates-retire-to-curb-far-right-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 14:08:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔对近期数据表示欢迎，但美联储需要更多信心才能降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/powell-welcomes-recent-data-but-fed-needs-more-confidence-to-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，最新的经济数据显示通胀正在重回下行通道，但他补充说，官员们希望在降低利率之前看到更多证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/powell-welcomes-recent-data-but-fed-needs-more-confidence-to-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:48:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
